videos.description: Ky Bowman spins free and sinks a difficult 3-pointer to give BC a 12-11 lead over Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: BC's Bowman spins and sinks 3

videos.description: Ky Bowman turns the corner and flushes a one-handed dunk.
